summary: This is an email correspondence from July 9, 2021, transmitting a federal trial subpoena for student records from the School District of West Palm Beach regarding a student with a specific date of birth who attended Survivors Charter School. The document indicates ongoing legal proceedings requiring educational records.

events.title: Issuance of Federal Trial Subpoena
events.description: A federal trial subpoena was issued for student records from the School District of West Palm Beach regarding a student with a specific date of birth who attended Survivors Charter School.

keyFacts: A federal trial subpoena was issued on July 6, 2021, for student records.
The subpoena targeted the School District of West Palm Beach.
The records sought pertain to a student with a specific date of birth who attended Survivors Charter School.
The email transmitting the subpoena is dated July 9, 2021, and marked as high importance.
The document indicates an active legal proceeding requiring educational records as evidence.
